Name: CM-Install
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for Installing & Configuring the Infrastructure

Name: CM-SQL
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for Installing & Configuring the Site DB

Name: CM-SSI
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for Installing Site System Servers

Name: CM-NA
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used to retrieve content from the DP

Name: CM-CLIDC
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used to install the Client Agent on Domain Controllers

Name: CM-CLIMS
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used to install the Client Agent on Member Servers

Name: CM-CLIWS
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used to install the Client Agent on Workstations

Name: CM-SRS
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for Installing & Configuring SQL Reporting Services

Name: CM-OSDCap
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for Capturing the reference image

Name: CM-OSDTSL
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for writing back Task Seq Logs during OSD

Name: CM-DomJoin
DESCRIPTION: ConfigMgr (SCCM) Account used for joining computers to the domain during OSD
